Paper locator
=============

http://david-peter.de/pl

Paper locator is an easy and universal interface to get immediate access to scientific papers.

Tired of manually extracting journal, volume and page from a reference and searching the publisher websites manually? Paper locator does all the work for you. Just copy a text sample containing the reference and select if you want to see the abstract page or the document direcly (press enter).

Try one of the following:
  [1] R. B. Laughlin, Phys. Rev. Lett. 50, 1395 (1983).
  prl 17 1133
  arXiv:quant-ph/9707021
  lained in Nature Physics 1, 23 by Imm

